      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready for the road? This car is in fair condition and offers a great, budget-friendly option for anyone needing reliable transportation. It shows some honest signs of its journey, but it\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to keep on going for its next owner!",
