    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive care. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly perfect example that looks and drives like a brand-new car.",
