    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example benefits from a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a recently calibrated dual-VANOS unit, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with precision. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to maintain chassis integrity. Power is managed via the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a 3.62 final drive. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-enjoyed enthusiast car, the suspension is taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. A purist-spec machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean interior. Well-maintained engine. Recent service completed. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
